{"tid":527531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"減肥後加埋都有689磅 癡肥情侶11年來首嚐敦倫","createTime":"2018-01-12T18:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T00:46:58.000Z","uid":157545,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0c99ef5fb2624e94a5f01bd1f684269465c417","tid":527531,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T18:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180112/large/1515739349_f919.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180112%2Flarge%2F1515739349_f919.jpg&h=3c82db43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180112/large/1515739110_254b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180112%2Flarge%2F1515739110_254b.jpg&h=07b2eaa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我們以往未曾歡愛過，但現在我們可以了。」美國密蘇里州一對加起來重達1,256磅癡肥男女，因身型龐大，相交11年來都無法一嚐翻雲覆雨的滋味，他們最後決心減肥，減去合共574磅，才終可以享受魚水之歡。<br />\n<br />\n42歲的薩頓 (Lee Sutton)重714磅，39歲女友凱澤 (Rena Kiser)就重542磅，他們在電視節目《我的600磅生活》(My 600lb Life)中講述減肥經歷。<br />\n兩人11年前在減肥中心認識繼而相戀，共同生活，薩頓因太肥而無法離開睡床，最初是由凱澤照顧他，但凱澤近年體重亦飆升而自身難保，無法再照顧男友，要靠薩頓的姐妹每天上門協助他們日常起居。凱澤坦言大感尷尬，「我們到現在仍生存，是因為薩頓的姐妹每天都來幫我們」。<br />\n兩人決心要減肥，由密蘇里州前往德州求醫，醫生表示他們已肥到有生命危險，若再不減肥，生命會進入倒數階段。他們要先嚴格控制飲食，減去一定磅數以便再做胃繞道手術（Gastric Bypass Surgery）。<br />\n不過手術後並非一帆風順，薩頓繼續大吃大喝，令減到數磅，更壞的是，薩頓變得暴力，令兩人關係轉差，直至凱澤威脅要分手，薩頓才承諾改過。<br />\n減肥需要動力。兩人得悉減肥後可以享受魚水之歡，令他們努力不懈，終於在進行胃繞道手術一年後，薩頓減了303磅至411磅，凱澤就減了271磅至278磅，一對情人終於可交歡。薩頓更說，一旦達到理想目標就會向凱澤求婚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180112/large/1515739108_d3c4.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180112%2Flarge%2F1515739108_d3c4.jpg&d=NH1cLd6b0HR8c04Itq7TQC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=30866a96\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180112/large/1515739108_d3c4.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180112/large/1515739107_14d8.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180112%2Flarge%2F1515739107_14d8.jpg&d=NH1cLd6b0HR8c04Itq7TQC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=cf2eb3b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180112/large/1515739107_14d8.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df547aff9eade249533568e86862589e0a75d5d","tid":527531,"uid":53794,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"快啲死 兩座垃圾"},{"pid":"6d9dfc346ebe7baab6e1bea45bbe0d4ccda1bc43","tid":527531,"uid":119783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T19:36:54.000Z","msg":"係愛阿"},{"pid":"c00ced831fc7aa8056545e4f925c9eba3c44ed9c","tid":527531,"uid":144784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T19:37:54.000Z","msg":"689<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e041739c18480743e4627f24c9c7856a1474fac","tid":527531,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T19:57:05.000Z","msg":"瘦身男女"},{"pid":"de52490b93e0a507ffa059fe75fc964b342e64ba","tid":527531,"uid":129664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T21:30:31.000Z","msg":"點解兩個可以唔使做嘢都生活到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d093112c32949e3f1644e097e4b887f1aa1ede","tid":527531,"uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"